URI scheme name: tttps

Status: Provisional

Applications/protocols:
TLS TimeToken Secure Protocol (TTTPS).
A cryptographic temporal ordering proof
protocol augmenting TLS 1.3 with
Proof-of-Time records.
Specified in draft-helmprotocol-tttps-04.

Contact:
Heime Jorgen
heime.jorgen&proton.me

Author/Change controller:
Heime Jorgen, Kenosian

References:
draft-helmprotocol-tttps-04
https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/
draft-helmprotocol-tttps/

Scheme syntax:
tttps://host[:port][/path][?query]
Identical to https:// syntax.
Transport: TLS 1.3 + PoT frame.